VarAttributes.CATDESC: Ephemeris Time of the start  of the accumulation for this measurement.
VarAttributes.VAR_NOTES: This is the Ephemeris Time saved as a TT2000 CDF Variable.  The difference between the ET value and the TT value is less than a millisecond.  The ET time values have an accuracy of no greater than 3 milliseconds hence it was determined that there was no reason to convert the ET values into TT.

VarAttributes.CATDESC: FHeDU: Helium flux spectrograms in energy, by telescope in sector order (multi-spin accums plotted at end of accum)
VarAttributes.VAR_NOTES: The Helium component is measured in the first 9 (per REM) channels of this data product. The last 11 channels have values of a default value.
